<item>
            <title>[LU-3812] Interop 2.4.0&lt;-&gt;2.5 failure on test suite sanity-scrub test_10b: Expect &apos;paused&apos;, but got &apos;stopped&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3812</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/9a665dec-09ee-11e3-ad93-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/9a665dec-09ee-11e3-ad93-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_10b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(9) Expect &apos;paused&apos;, but got &apos;stopped&apos;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-scrub 10b&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>server: lustre-master tag-2.4.91 build #1627&lt;br/&gt;
client: 2.4.0</environment>
